        <abstract> 
<p>Chancellor of the Exchequer has ordered £1000 for the publication of the <hi rend="italic">Zoology</hi>. Would like to meet JR to ask his advice on one or two points.</p> 
            <p>Thanks for his long account of the climate of North America.</p>
